STATE
v.
Tyrone JOHNSON. No. 53P04-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 17, 2006. William P. Hart, Senior Deputy Attorney General, William Graham, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 12th day of July 2006 by Defendant for "Petition for Plain Error Review N.C.G.S. 7A-28(B)(1)(2)(3)(4)":

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 17th day of August 2006."
